; By Car * [[:en:Ise Expressway|Ise Expressway]]: About 8 minutes (3.35 km) north from {{ill|Ise Nishi IC|ja|伊勢西インターチェンジ|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ise Nishi IC|qq=}} via {{ill|Mie Prefectural Route 32|ja|三重県道32号伊勢磯部線|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mie Prefectural Route 32|qq=}} (Mikimoto Road). == References == {{Reflist}}
